OL,3,CPrime Minister to commit to 2.5% for
OL,4,Cdefence spending within days
OL,6,FThe prime minister is expected to
OL,7,Fcommit in coming days to increasing
OL,8,Fdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP by the
OL,9,Fend of the decade and possibly much
OL,10,Fsooner.
OL,12,FThe effective deadline for an
OL,13,Fannouncement is Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,14,Fhistoric meeting with President Trump
OL,15,Fon Thursday.
OL,17,FSenior British officials believe it is
OL,18,Fimperative that he demonstrates to
OL,19,FPresident Trump that the UK is doing
OL,20,Fits part in reducing Europe's defence
OL,21,Fand security dependence on the US.
