OL,3,CPrime Minister to commit to 2.5% for
OL,4,Cdefence spending within days
OL,6,FHowever, reinforcing the strength of a
OL,7,Fstretched and depleted UK military has
OL,8,Fbecome the prime minister's priority,
OL,9,Fespecially since President Trump
OL,10,Fsidelined Europe in talks with
OL,11,FPresident Putin on ending Russia's
OL,12,Fillegal invasion of Ukraine.
OL,14,FThose close to the prime minister say
OL,15,Fthat the election of Trump has
OL,16,F"inaugurated a new political era",
OL,17,Fwhich will involve - among other
OL,18,Fpolicy shifts - much greater spending
OL,19,Fby European countries on defence and
OL,20,Fsecurity.
