OL,3,CPrime Minister to commit to 2.5% for
OL,4,Cdefence spending within days
OL,6,FAt the moment, the UK spends 2.3% of
OL,7,FGPD or national income on defence. But
OL,8,Fwhen expenditure on the nuclear
OL,9,Fdeterrent is stripped out,
OL,10,Fconventional military spending is just
OL,11,F1.5% of GDP, which is below NATO's 2%
OL,12,Fthreshold and equivalent to what
OL,13,FPortugal spends.
OL,15,F"Obviously you can't ignore our
OL,16,Fnuclear spend, but you can see how
OL,17,Fstretched are our conventional
OL,18,Fresources," said an influential
OL,19,Fofficial.
