OL,6,FThere is however no spare cash in the
OL,7,FTreasury's kitty to do anything.
OL,9,FOn March 26 the Office for Budget
OL,10,FResponsibility will confirm that the
OL,11,Fchancellor is breaching her fiscal
OL,12,Frules, and will have to find billions
OL,13,Fof pounds from spending cuts or
OL,14,Fstealth tax increases, such as
OL,15,Fextending the freeze on income tax
OL,16,Fthresholds.
