OL,6,FShe will then announce a package of
OL,7,Fspending and tax measures to reduce
OL,8,Fborrowing that are not supposed to be
OL,9,Fa budget but are increasingly being
OL,10,Fdescribed as a budget by officials.
OL,12,FIf the additional #6bn for defence was
OL,13,Fsplit evenly between capital and
OL,14,Fcurrent or day-to-day spending, it
OL,15,Fwould deplete fiscal "headroom" less
OL,16,Fthan channelling all the cash to
OL,17,Fcurrent spending.
